<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="424" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="23.[151,1437,358,601]" pageId="23" pageNumber="424">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,466,493]" pageId="23" pageNumber="424">Distribution.</emphasis>
This species was previously recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[856,1003,467,493]" name="Saudi Arabia" pageId="23" pageNumber="424">Saudi Arabia</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Dawah, H. A. &amp; Abdullah, M. A." box="[1048,1355,467,494]" pageId="23" pageNumber="424" pagination="383 - 394" refId="ref28384" refString="Dawah, H. A. &amp; Abdullah, M. A. (2006) The Ephydridae (Diptera: Brachycera: Muscomorpha) of south-western Saudi Arabia. Fauna of Arabia, 21, 383 - 394." type="journal article" year="2006">Dawah &amp; Abdullah (2006)</bibRefCitation>
. It was described from 
<collectingCountry box="[328,398,503,529]" name="Sudan" pageId="23" pageNumber="424">Sudan</collectingCountry>
(Senaar) and recorded from the Afrotropical Region: 
<collectingCountry box="[1005,1071,503,529]" name="Niger" pageId="23" pageNumber="424">Niger</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1081,1182,503,529]" name="Tanzania" pageId="23" pageNumber="424">Tanzania</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[1237,1360,503,529]" name="Zimbabwe" pageId="23" pageNumber="424">Zimbabwe</collectingCountry>
. There are some specimens in NMWC collected from 
<collectingCountry box="[678,754,539,565]" name="Kenya" pageId="23" pageNumber="424">Kenya</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[765,849,539,565]" name="Nigeria" pageId="23" pageNumber="424">Nigeria</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[902,984,539,565]" name="Yemen" pageId="23" pageNumber="424">Yemen</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
